titles.title: Commending the Kentucky National Guard for its service to the Commonwealth of Kentucky and the citizens of the United States.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR E2103)
Referred to the House Committee on Armed Services.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Military Personnel.

bill.summary:
10/10/2007--Introduced.
Commends and recognizes the achievements of members of certain sections of the 1st and 2nd Battalions of the Kentucky Army National Guard for their service in Iraq.
